spec_data.Name: exim-doc
spec_data.Description:
Exim is a mail transport agent (MTA) developed at the University of
Cambridge for use on Unix systems connected to the Internet. This
package contains the documentation for Exim, also available on the
web at http://www.exim.org/
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 04:08:28 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Documentation for the exim mail transfer agent
